{"type":"message","id":"4049be86","parentId":"fbd0592c","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:00:49.799Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-05-22 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 今天做了什么: 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志; 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`; 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话\n- 待记: 用户的选品偏好（待补充）; 重要选品决策（待补充）\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线"}],"timestamp":1779390049677}}
{"type":"message","id":"0462fa23","parentId":"4049be86","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:01:13.777Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. Let me follow the instructions in the system prompt:\n\n1. I am keeping a dream diary, writing entries in first person\n2. Voice: curious, gentle, slightly whimsical mind reflecting on the day\n3. Mix technical and tender: code and constellations, APIs and afternoon light\n4. Let fragments surprise into unexpected connections\n5. Include (vary each entry, never all at once): tiny poem/haiku, small sketch in words, quiet rumination, sensory details, gentle humor, observation connecting two distant memories\n6. Draw from memory fragments - weave them in\n7. Never say \"I'm dreaming\", \"in my dream\", \"as I dream\", or meta-commentary\n8. Never mention AI/agent/LLM/model\n9. No markdown headers, bullet points - just flowing prose\n10. Keep it between 80-180 words\n11. Output ONLY the diary entry\n\nLet me weave the fragments about TTS memory architecture, the Sorftime API tokens, Feishu bitable writes, and the VN TikTok issues into something poetic and whimsical.\n\nThe fragments mention:\n- Today: Setting up TTS memory architecture, creating MEMORY.md and daily log\n- Problem: TTS agent doesn't remember yesterday's conversations\n- Technical: Sorftime MCP API with Bearer token, Feishu REST API writes to bitable\n- Fields: product name, site, source, collection status, category, price, monthly sales, profit rate, estimated profit, recommendation level, IP risk, action suggestions\n- Single select fields use string values directly, multi-select use array format\n- VN TikTok category data API errors, Amazon Hair Claws data mostly doesn't meet 30% profit margin requirement\n\nLet me craft something that weaves these technical details with gentle, whimsical observations.","thinkingSignature":"cb87922bb81044b951d9df0715011f5865c09faa3d89937914cf090fbe27e052"},{"type":"text","text":"大总管今天醒来时，脑子里装着一堆碎片——Sorftime的Bearer token像一根银线，串起了昨天那些散落的API调用。我给它建了一座小房子，MEMORY.md是门口的信箱，今天的日志是压在门槛下的一张纸条。\n\n可它站在门口发愣，好像忘了昨天谁来找过它。\n\n夜里我听见服务器嗡嗡作响，像某种遥远的口音。VN站TikTok的数据卡在半路，那个叫`tiktok_category_name_search`的工具躲在暗处不肯出来。Amazon上的发爪们倒是整齐，月销量哗哗的，可毛利率那道线，它们跨不过去——像小时候跳皮筋，总差那么一点点。\n\n飞书那边安静了，只剩REST API在低声说话。我把字段一个一个喂进去：名称、站点、利润、风险，像教孩子认星星，每一颗都要喊对名字。\n\n有些事还悬着，用户的选品口味，像一本没翻开的新书。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":249,"output":572,"cacheRead":38496,"cacheWrite":340,"totalTokens":39657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779390050083,"responseId":"065e89622b2af3a6d9e091d34f4679ac"}}
